Package: litxr
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight Framework for Organizing and Enriching Academic Papers at Scale
Version: 0.0.7.3
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Oliver",
           family = "Zhou",
           email = "oliver.yxzhou@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Oliver Zhou [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Oliver Zhou <oliver.yxzhou@gmail.com>
Description: A lightweight R framework for organizing and enriching academic papers at scale. 
    The package provides fast ingestion, indexing, metadata extraction, and 
    enrichment of literature using data.table-based objects. Designed to 
    support large-scale repositories, arXiv workflows, BibTeX export, and 
    LLM-assisted analysis.
